{"commentv2": 1, "number": 1, "id": 2412046, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Saper89", "body": "He is NPC for turning in quests that can drop from Class Hall followers missions. If he is currently on mission, you can't end them and you need to wait for his mission ended, take loot and then (without sending him on another mission) walk out - walk in to spawn him near table.", "date": "2016-09-23T11:14:33-05:00", "rating": 21, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "This is ridiculous! I've send him on a mission and he was still there the whole time. Then I accepted the quest to search for another artifact (discipline), turned in the quest for making the choice and while reading the following quests text he despawned. This is what I call \"bad design\"! (btw, relogging did not solve the issue)", "creationdate": "2017-02-11T08:01:45-06:00", "id": 1031863, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2412046, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "pros4c", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "It's an understatement to say that this is annoying.", "creationdate": "2017-04-24T00:39:11-05:00", "id": 1047451, "rating": 1, "commentid": 2412046, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "remid0d0s0", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Came here to look for this. I had the quest \"A \"Noble\" Event to turn in, but he was not there; even with no follower missions active at all. Did as you said: Walk Out & Walk In and poof, he was there. Thank you!", "creationdate": "2018-07-27T19:28:31-05:00", "id": 1124083, "rating": 0, "commentid": 2412046, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Artio", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dat